How to use 
==========

pip install myhydra

Available Functions
===================


add_project_metadata
-----------------------
Arguments -

project - 
           Name of the project Ex: RTDP
app     - 
           Name of the application Ex: V4 Device Lookup Model
dataset -
           Name of the Dataset Ex: X1_Households
jobid   -
           JobID  Ex: Databricks JobId
dayid   -
           dayid being processed (Optional Parameter)

post_job_status
-----------------------
Arguments -

environment -
              Provide environment value. It will take one of the value ['DEV', 'QA', 'STAG', 'PROD']. For any other value it throws ValueError Exception
status      - 
              Provide job status value. It will take one of the value ['START', 'SUCCESS', 'FAILURE']. For any other value it throws ValueError Exception
source      - 
              Data source value. Example: RTDP D2A
input       - 
              Optional Parameter
output      - 
             Optional Parameter

add_dq_metric
-----------------------
Arguments -

type      - 
            "COUNT" / "DISTINCT" / "NULL"
Name      - 
            Name of the column + type ("Col_1_Count")
value     - 
            Metric value
status    - 
            True / False
threshold - 
            Optional Parameter (Value Ex: 0.5)
percent   - 
            Optional Parameter (Value Ex: 0.0)

post_dq_metrics
-----------------------
Arguments -

status    -
            True / False (if all metrics status are True then True else False)



